PRIMARY BEDROOM HAS TRAY CEILING, CROWN MOLDING, RECESSED LIGHTING, DUAL WALK-IN FITTED CLOSETS , DOOR LEADING TO LANAI.  PRIMARY BATHROOM HAS DUAL SINKS/VANITY, SOAKING TUB, FLOOR TO CEILING TILE IN SHOWER, SEPARATE WATER CLOSET.  GUEST BEDROOM 1 HAS POCKET DOORS, FITTED CLOSET, BUILT-INS & RECESSED LIGHTING. GUEST BEDROOM 2 HAS FITTED CLOSETS.  GUEST BEDROOM 3 USED AS OFFICE. ALL MEASUREMENTS ARE DEEMED ACCURATE AND SHOULD BE INDEPENDENTLY VERIFIED.  VALENCIA FALLS IS AN ACTIVE 55+ COMMUNITY WITH A 25,000 SQ FT CLUBHOUSE WHICH HAS A CAFE WITH INDOOR/OUTDOOR DINING, GRAND SOCIAL HALL, CARD ROOMS, FITNESS FACILITY, AEROBICS STUDIO, ART/PHOTOGRAPHY STUDIO, RESORT-STYLE POOL, RESISTANCE POOL, SPA, HAR-TRU TENNIS COURTS, PICKLEBALL COURTS, BOCCE, OVER 35 CLUBS AND ORGANIZATION TO WHICH YOU CAN BELONG AND SO MUCH MORE.
